#. type: Content of: <article><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: English/Compare_dirs.xml:170
msgid ""
"In tabular view, each file or folder in the result is listed in a row. This "
"is the default view. Here's an example:"
msgstr ""
"In tabular view, each file or folder in the result is listed in a row.Questa "
"è la visualizzazione predefinita.Ecco un esempio:"

